<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Gonna answer this MONKEY!<br>
                                                                                      Monkey King<p>

  Bard has more down sides then good;<br>
  1. They are feeble in strengh compared to Pallys, SKs, Warrios etc.<p>

**True we aren't as strong or have as many hit points. We dont need as much strength and I let the ranger taunt when fighting and I rarely get hit.<p>

  2. Their Magic (songs) are almost usless "OHhhh ! Jig is zing through my body, how wonderful !"<p>

** Jig is a low level song but it can be useful at higher levels if its a long fight and everyone is  too low on stamia to fight their best.<p>

  3. Thier speical skill are not as good, unlike Pally's Lay on Hand, SK's Harm Touch<p>

** Bard "special Skills" are differnt. We can run faster than sow with drum and we get the sought after mana song at 32. Great charm songs and buff songs. We aren't really big healers. We have too many other uses.<p>

  4. As Gaile was saying Bards beates all other melee class, I'll tell you who beats all the melee class; monks,<br>
  pallys, <br>
  warriors. <br>
That was someones personal opinion who cares what you think!<p>

  5. Have you have seen a Bard say, HEALING AND BUFFING AT GATE, I don't think so...<p>

  You might look cool in the SS and Lambent armor, but your not as good as you think you are.<p>

*** Bards are made for grouping with. We only work in groups. I occasionly help some lost soul or find a body. Nope I don't have to worry about being bugged for a buff or TP. =)<br>
I think thats a very big upside. I know its bad when your a druid trying to fight and you have tells during fight please tp me or sow me and your trying to benefit your group. You don't have mana to sow all of continent of Antonica.<p>

Anything else you don't know didley about?<p>

Kit</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
