s health regen rate and hymn of rest can gain mass hp in very very short time at this time i my self have 560hp and it takes me just about 1 min to get 400 bac so needless to say we have best regen in game, the equip ratio for bards matches that of almost even a pally since the new singing steel has been found along with weapon ratio we hit well doge better and we SING who cant use a good tune now and then right, we are thy absoulute BEST choice for a group with mana regen, HP regen, Sta regen, invis, levi,underwater breathing, and MANY many more songs as such i dont see how u could live with out us. in closing i would just like to let u no that we ARE the BEST class in game and we are growing more and more and soon will be the only class u will see in the game so just remember bards are GODS and if u or any one else insults the works of a BARD i would make it my personal afront to hunt u down and KICK UR but ). OHHH i forgot bards have a pricise sence of timeing and accuracy in so haveing thy ability to play notes for different songs at once im not a master of this art yet so im only able to play 4 at once in battle in doing so getting affects from all the songs at once some may call this ability toggleing or twisting i call it weaveing ) so those are thy reasons why bards are so cool and i am sorry for this message being sooo long and knowing most ppl would post a message below mine saying a buncha bad stuff about me but i dont mind cause im a bard and we dont worrie about lesser beings feeble remarks hehe agian sry about the leangth of this message<hr>Celtix En'Vec the bard</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
